Please note: This projet has been developed as an assessment for an undergraduate unit: EES4100 - Operating Systems and Network Programming at Victoria University,Melbourne, Australia. It was created only for eductaional purposes. 

The project consists of a bridge application, whereby data is read from a Modbus server and re transmitted to a BACnet client. To achieve this the application simultaneously operates as both a Modbus client and BACnet server in seperate 
threads. 
